💚 I am so thankful for my mum👩‍👧. A candle🕯 can keep a room glow with its light, but a mum like her makes all my days bright!💡🌞 My mum 👩‍🦰 inspired me to dream God-sized💥 dreams, speaks truth & encouragement in difficult seasons & reminds me how I shine🌟. She has made a difference in my life greatly 😇 .
Mothers are incredible creation of God 😇. My mum spent her life pouring selflessly & sacrificially into me. When I was young 👶👧, she carried diaper bags, waterbottles, lunchboxes,🎒, books & bandages. When I grew up👩, she gracefully carry all my burdens, worries, cares & concerns! .
Being a mom is like no other job in the world & her job is never done. Unlike a typical 9-to-5 job, motherhood is a “career” often motivated by pure & unwavering 🔥love. Mum cares & nurtures me.🎋 She knows me deeply & loves me dearly, all the while instilling the importance of a love, empathy & compassion for others. She takes her role seriously, praying for me, guiding me & serving me as a beautiful reflection of God’s unfailing & unrelenting love. .
👩‍🦰 Mum, words can’t explain how I feel. I appreciate your presence & existence. Who you are is irreplaceable. You’re an awesome mother🦸‍♀️ You’re a virtuous wife 👨‍👩‍👧 You're a gift of love that fills my heart & my life. I’m so grateful for all that you poured into me. You showed me what love feels like & made me believe I could take on the world. You always saw the best in me & hoped the best for me. You were selfless over & over & over again. I wouldn’t be here without you! I would be so lost without you! Thank you from the bottom of my heart. I’m so privileged to call you, "Mom"!🌹

10 times! My mother is a great cook and an in-kueh-dible mentor. Learning to cook traditional Peranakan dishes from her, like Ayam Buah Keluak, and to make Nonya Kueh, was a great bonding activity for us. Preparing the rempah (spice paste) from scratch was a tedious, labour-intensive process, but also an enriching experience for me. My mother takes an organic culinary approach with no shortcuts. When making Kueh Salat, we painstaking squeeze the juice from fresh Pandan leaves and the blue dye from the butter pea flower. She says the attention to detail will contribute to the ultimate sensory taste and texture. Through this experience, I also picked up an important life lesson from her – To get the best results, do not take shortcuts. To celebrate Mother’s Day, I hope she can take a break from the kitchen and indulge in a shopping spree at @wheelockplace ! @ernestwyy @mursjid @thereal_meowsyy 👩🏻‍🍳👩‍👧‍👦❤️🛍

Can’t wait to pamper my mum with a shopping spree ❤️ My mum is special because of her unconventional way of loving me. During my university days, when I am always studying late at night till 2-3am, she will “scold” me for studying till the wee hours. No matter is it primary school, secondary school, junior college or when choosing university courses, she always make sure she’s there to “nag” at me and “challenge” my choices. Now that I’m married, she’s still there to “complain” about the food i cook and how i manage household matters. 
But i know deep down in her heart, she love me for who I am. She’s my lifelong mentor. No matter what time it is or how busy she is, I can count on her to be there for me. I’m very fortunate that I can always turn to her and there was never a time where I felt that I'm alone. I'm grateful for her and I appreciate the role she play in my life ❤️ she show me her capacity of loving someone in a way I never would have imagined, she show me how big her heart would get, she show me that being a mum is the best job in the world and she wouldn't want it any other way ❤️ My mum is the best, she’s my biggest supporter and always have my best interest at heart.
